{"tid":1784093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"噢~ 聖誕節派聖誕卡~","createTime":"2019-12-15T11:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:42:41.000Z","uid":20589,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a379d6c54fc883267a8ddd2b1e988d6326f99f7c","tid":1784093,"uid":20589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"就快到聖誕節啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔咗一段時間，我地又返嚟派聖誕卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年份表格問題多咗，但神秘驚喜同樣亦都多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家不妨講出心事，我地會為你分憂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家放馬過嚟，唔使怕醜嚟填表要聖誕卡啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接受填寫日期：  2019年12月15日 － 2019年12月18日(3:00am)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n名額暫時不限<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n越早填越早收到聖誕卡，寫聖誕卡需時，亦未必會寄比大家，請耐心等候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＊所有個人資料只會用喺寫聖誕卡，唔會公開同用喺其他用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預祝各位巴絲打聖誕心想事成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338560a8e56160b5cac7c0c9b6906a3f666d5690","tid":1784093,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1afd284e856462d5958f5e2e627c8e0a67a9bb96","tid":1784093,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42883362a4dc1abce6ecd9d769b11453dd5d3